+!> \brief Select the periodic ACP forward/reverse mesh contraction.
+!>
+!> DENSE is the permanent Part-I complete-mesh and full-difference-set oracle. STREAMED folds
+!> bounded forward k batches immediately and contracts compact projector images directly with
+!> CP2K's existing sparse real-space density images in the reverse pass. QUALIFY executes both
+!> routes, compares every raw response at a strict relative tolerance, and applies STREAMED once.
+!> \param tb tblite state carrying the public CP2K input value
+!> \return selected ACP mesh contraction
+! **************************************************************************************************
+   INTEGER FUNCTION tb_gxtb_acp_mesh_mode(tb) RESULT(mesh_mode)
+
+      TYPE(tblite_type), INTENT(IN)                      :: tb
+
